R. H. CROWLEY, PETITIONER, v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 45648] [105 C. Cls. 97;

329 U. S. —]

Government contract; decision of resident engineer final, under the contract, as to quality of materials.

Plaintiff’s petition for writ of certiorari denied, by the Supreme Court October 14, 1946.
